cmnsvycbl0000p0tvpuya1nsv	cmnogbz5500040ctvk0h77tjv	Install SQL Server 2019 in a windows server in Azure Cloud environment . It should have backup as well,	null	DATABASE	COMPLETE	12	0	\N	{\n  "title": "SQL Server 2019 Installation with Backup Configuration on Azure Windows Server",\n  "domain": "DATABASE",\n  "objective": "Deploy a fully configured Microsoft SQL Server 2019 instance on an Azure-hosted Windows Server virtual machine, including instance configuration, security hardening, and an automated backup solution to ensure data protection and recoverability in a production-grade Azure environment.",\n  "in_scope": [\n    "Provision and configure an appropriately sized Azure Windows Server VM suitable for SQL Server 2019 workloads",\n    "Install and configure Microsoft SQL Server 2019 with appropriate edition and feature selection based on customer requirements",\n    "Configure SQL Server instance settings including memory allocation, tempdb optimisation, and authentication mode",\n    "Apply SQL Server security hardening including sa account management, surface area configuration, and Windows Firewall rules",\n    "Configure automated SQL Server backup jobs using SQL Server Agent covering full, differential, and transaction log backups",\n    "Set up Azure Blob Storage as the backup destination for offsite retention of database backup files",\n    "Validate the installation and backup solution via test backup and restore operation with documented results"\n  ],\n  "out_of_scope": [\n    "Database schema design, creation of application databases, or data migration from existing systems",\n    "SQL Server licensing procurement — customer must supply a valid SQL Server 2019 licence or Azure Hybrid Benefit entitlement",\n    "Azure networking design including VNet, NSG, or ExpressRoute configuration beyond VM-level firewall rules",\n    "High availability or disaster recovery configuration such as Always On Availability Groups or Log Shipping",\n    "Application integration, ODBC/DSN configuration, or connection string setup for third-party applications",\n    "Ongoing SQL Server administration, monitoring, or managed DBA services post-deployment"\n  ],\n  "assumptions": [\n    "Customer holds an active Azure subscription with sufficient quota and permissions to provision virtual machines and storage accounts",\n    "Customer has a valid SQL Server 2019 licence or is eligible for Azure Hybrid Benefit; licensing cost is not included in this engagement",\n    "The Azure VM size and storage tier will be selected to meet the customer's stated workload requirements prior to provisioning",\n    "Remote access to the Azure VM via RDP or Azure Bastion will be available to the engineer throughout the engagement",\n    "Customer accepts that backup retention policy and schedule will be defined and agreed upon before implementation begins"\n  ],\n  "prerequisites": [\n    "Active Azure subscription with Owner or Contributor role access provided to the engineer",\n    "SQL Server 2019 installation media or product key made available prior to engagement start",\n    "Written confirmation of backup retention requirements, schedule frequency, and target Azure Storage Account or permission to create one",\n    "Agreed VM sizing and Azure region selection documented before provisioning commences"\n  ],\n  "deliverables": [\n    "Fully installed and configured SQL Server 2019 instance running on an Azure Windows Server VM",\n    "Automated backup jobs configured in SQL Server Agent with full, differential, and transaction log schedules targeting Azure Blob Storage",\n    "Post-installation configuration document detailing instance settings, service accounts, firewall rules, and backup policy",\n    "Evidence of a successful test backup and restore operation confirming backup integrity and recoverability"\n  ],\n  "currency": "AUD",\n  "price": 1200,\n  "hours_min": 6,\n  "hours_max": 12,\n  "milestone_count": 1\n}	{"price": 1200, "title": "S