t", "Customer accepts that backup retention policy and schedule will be defined and agreed upon before implementation begins"], "deliverables": ["Fully installed and configured SQL Server 2019 instance running on an Azure Windows Server VM", "Automated backup jobs configured in SQL Server Agent with full, differential, and transaction log schedules targeting Azure Blob Storage", "Post-installation configuration document detailing instance settings, service accounts, firewall rules, and backup policy", "Evidence of a successful test backup and restore operation confirming backup integrity and recoverability"], "out_of_scope": ["Database schema design, creation of application databases, or data migration from existing systems", "SQL Server licensing procurement — customer must supply a valid SQL Server 2019 licence or Azure Hybrid Benefit entitlement", "Azure networking design including VNet, NSG, or ExpressRoute configuration beyond VM-level firewall rules", "High availability or disaster recovery configuration such as Always On Availability Groups or Log Shipping", "Application integration, ODBC/DSN configuration, or connection string setup for third-party applications", "Ongoing SQL Server administration, monitoring, or managed DBA services post-deployment"], "prerequisites": ["Active Azure subscription with Owner or Contributor role access provided to the engineer", "SQL Server 2019 installation media or product key made available prior to engagement start", "Written confirmation of backup retention requirements, schedule frequency, and target Azure Storage Account or permission to create one", "Agreed VM sizing and Azure region selection documented before provisioning commences"], "milestone_count": 1}	\N	ACTIVE	\N	\N	[{"at": "2026-04-10T12:56:26.408Z", "event": "CONTRACT_CREATED", "detail": "Contract created from awarded tender", "actor_id": "cmnogbz5500040ctvk0h77tjv"}, {"at": "2026-04-10T12:58:33.668Z", "event": "NOTE_ADDED", "detail": "I will start this next 